## ü§ù Contributing

### **Development Setup**
```bash
# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/GaiaForge/tanzania-hive-monitor.git
cd tanzania-hive-monitor

# Install PlatformIO
pip install platformio

# Build project
pio run -e adafruit_feather_nrf52840

# Upload to device
pio run -e adafruit_feather_nrf52840 -t upload
```

### **Hardware Requirements**
- Adafruit Feather nRF52840 Express
- BME280 sensor breakout
- MAX9814 microphone module
- PCF8523 RTC breakout
- SH1106 OLED display
- MicroSD card module
- LiPo battery and solar panel

